data.description:
Welcome to this spacious family home that offers an inviting and elegant ambiance from the moment you step inside. The gleaming dark hardwood flooring and the beautifully crafted wrought iron spindles on the staircase create a striking first impression. The large kitchen, adorned with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, is perfect for culinary enthusiasts and features a private dining area, ideal for family gatherings.

Additionally, this home boasts a private office with charming French doors, providing a secluded space for work or study. The stone gas and electric fireplace adds a touch of warmth and coziness to the living area. With a huge media room that can easily be converted into a fifth bedroom, this home offers versatility and plenty of space for your family's needs.

The master closet is a standout feature, offering ample storage and organization with its built-in shelving. Step outside to the backyard, which is spacious enough for a pool, and you'll find yourself immersed in the beauty of a greenbelt walking trail, complete with a picturesque pond and fountain view. The balcony offers a serene spot to enjoy your morning coffee while witnessing the breathtaking sunrise, and it also provides a relaxing space to unwind in the evenings, overlooking the pond that wraps around the cul-de-sac.

Not only is this home a haven, but it is also situated in an amazing community. Multiple pools throughout the neighborhood offer refreshing retreats during the warm months, and the fitness center and South pool are conveniently located just a block away. For outdoor enthusiasts, Joe Pool Lake is only a few miles away, providing endless opportunities for recreation and relaxation. Furthermore, you'll find multiple shopping centers in close proximity, ensuring that your everyday needs are easily met.

This home truly offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and community, making it an exceptional opportunity for those seeking a remarkable place to call their own.

The location of your home sounds ideal for families with school-aged children. Being in close proximity to a highly regarded school district is definitely a major advantage. The fact that there's an elementary school just two blocks away makes it extremely convenient for families with young kids. Additionally, having an intermediate and high school within a 7-minute drive offers convenience and accessibility for students of all ages. It's great to know that your home is perfectly situated for a smooth transition into the new school year.

This property will be sold as is.
data.whatILove:
This home offers some remarkable features and ample storage options. Here's an updated description:

The master suite in this home is exceptionally spacious, providing you with a luxurious retreat within your own living space. With two AC units, comfort is ensured throughout the entire house, allowing you to regulate the temperature to your liking. Every room in the house is generously proportioned, ensuring that your family and guests have plenty of space to relax and unwind.

If storage is a priority for you, you'll be delighted to know that this home offers an incredible 19+ closets, providing ample room for organizing your belongings. The kitchen is designed with functionality in mind and boasts abundant storage space, allowing you to keep all your culinary essentials easily accessible.

The Jack and Jill bedrooms are an added highlight, each featuring two walk-in closets and their own dedicated dressing areas. These dressing areas include separate sinks and even additional shoe closets, making it convenient for multiple occupants to get ready simultaneously without sacrificing personal space.

With such thoughtfully designed storage solutions and spacious rooms throughout, your home ensures that you have all the room you need to live comfortably and efficiently.
